Package: scTorus
Type: Package
Title: Arrange Cells along a Pseudo Time
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jianxin Wang
Maintainer: Jianxin Wang <jianxinwang24@gmail.com>
Description: This tool takes a single cell data frame (scRNA-Seq or Vectra, etc) and arrange cells along a pseudo time line. It project ggplot2 plotting objects that can be used to make three plots
    A scatterplot showing cells arranged along a circle
    A heatmap showing the cell cycle marker expression levels or intensities
    A trajectory profile plot showing the dynamics of various cell cycle markers along the pseudo time line.
